Environment Setup:- 

Created Azure resources: Blob Storage, ADF, Databricks Workspace, Synapse Analytics SQL Pool

Uploaded raw CSV file to Blob Storage: iot-data/raw/sensor_data.csv

# Environment Setup ~

1- Create Azure Resources

- Azure Data Factory (ADF)

- Azure Databricks Workspace

- Azure Synapse Analytics workspace and dedicated SQL pool

- Azure Storage Account (for raw data)

2- Dataset Selection & Upload

Download IoT sensor dataset from Kaggle (e.g., Energy consumption)

Upload it to Azure Storage Account (Blob Storage)

Example structure:

/iot-data/raw/
  - sensor_data.csv

3- Link Services

Connect Storage Account to ADF, Databricks, and Synapse.

Set up Linked Services in ADF for Storage and Databricks.
